item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Software_License
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Software_License Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Billing_Item_Software_License data type contains general information relating to a single SoftLayer billing item for a software license. Local allowCancellationFlag Flag to check if a billing item can be cancelled. 1 = yes. 0 = no. Type: integer associatedBillingItemId This is sometimes populated for orphan billing items that are not attached to servers. Billing items like secondary portable IP addresses fit into this category.
